reviews.review_text: Barely a soundboard This sounds very much like a good audience tape.  The soundboard quality is either severely lacking in bass, or the microphones are picking up the audience more than ever before.  Soundboard actually kicks in at the second set.  In any case, all good except Far From Me which should be sent far, far away and never heard again.  5 Stars as usual plus 1 vote to bring back Donna.  Jer's thinking during Stella...already said Dust off those rusty Strings...what now?
